Inline "grep" with perl: print only login shells on pts/3, 5, and 7:
    [pv@trogdor ~]$ w | perl -ne '/pts\/[3,5,7]\s/ && print'
    pv       pts/3     06:06   23:10   0.05s  0.00s bash /home/pv/foo
    pv       pts/7     10:39    1:07m  0.54s  0.54s -bash

